{
  "text": "-Functions: A set of functions F the application called during the execution. -Call graph: A call graph, with nodes representing functions, and an edge from f to f if f calls f at least once during the execution. -Calling context tree: A calling context tree [CITATION_1] , with the root node representing the program's entry point and a node f as child of node f if f calls f in the same context at least once during its execution.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "6585851"
